      • parse

        abstract LogEntry parse​(byte version,
                        ReadableChecksumChannel channel,
                        LogPositionMarker marker,
                        CommandReaderFactory commandReaderFactory)
                 throws IOException
        Parses the next LogEntry read from the channel.
        Parameters:
        version - version this log entry is determined to be of.
        channel - ReadableChecksumChannel to read the data from.
        marker - LogPositionMarker marking the position in the channel that is the start of this entry.
        commandReaderFactory - CommandReaderFactory for retrieving a CommandReader for reading commands from, for log entry types that need that.
        Returns:
        the next LogEntry read and parsed from the channel.
        Throws:
        IOException - I/O error from channel or if data was read past the end of the channel.
